title: [1508521049] Best Restaurant: Yu & You, Secret Diner - Gordon Ramsay
description:
Ramsay reveals the second test on, chinese restaurant Yu & You, with the result of secret diner.

Gordon Ramsay in search of Britain's best restaurant. Top restaurants from around the UK compete to win the title.
